{"tid":1869441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網傳警員捐口罩予武漢 警方指與警隊無關 已作訓示","createTime":"2020-02-08T07:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T14:50:02.000Z","uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ceb9e1c469952712aaa51b1d0224b6c06e55ad","tid":1869441,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】網傳警員捐口罩予武漢 警方指屬私人捐贈 已作訓示<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3974371/org/e48cd192febd39b3d2048aa28590e66e.jpg/bgc2mUvu4T99FcqWz73YEBTu7oz-WXY5SCQMcEgkDHA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3974371%2Forg%2Fe48cd192febd39b3d2048aa28590e66e.jpg%2Fbgc2mUvu4T99FcqWz73YEBTu7oz-WXY5SCQMcEgkDHA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=7b23e10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網傳一盒順豐貨物的紙盒上，寫有「香港警察捐贈口罩520個，520（我愛你）」，而下款為「海港sir」，而票據上亦寫明「香港警察捐贈」，收件地址為湖北省武漢市江夏區第一人民醫院。網民質疑是否有警員以警方名義贈送口罩到武漢，並懷疑是由懲教署工業組（Correctional Services Industries）生產、主要供應政府部門的CSI口罩。警方表示，口罩是一名警員以個人身份購入的韓國口罩，並捐往武漢，而捐贈屬私人意願，警方已訓示該名警員。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應事件稱，警方經瞭解事件後，得悉一名警務人員以個人身份購入一批韓國口罩，並捐贈予武漢醫護人員。是次捐贈純屬該人員的私人意願，與警隊無關。 警方強調，上述的口罩並非由懲教署工業組(CSI )生產的口罩。 警方已經訓示有關人員，在未經許可下，不得以警隊名義作出任何捐贈行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3974025/org/dbd07a30abbdede4d35f76248906b453.jpg/8YIWX8IvGY1RP1VBVS1ZHeWtKYf0aZXe7cMjDO3DIww?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3974025%2Forg%2Fdbd07a30abbdede4d35f76248906b453.jpg%2F8YIWX8IvGY1RP1VBVS1ZHeWtKYf0aZXe7cMjDO3DIww%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8bf3117b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3974026/org/40b23b0aed0d79bebe03bf70b60f064c.jpg/VePIf3_WO3lw0pbUlC-v-WFeMZYCC3TcLxcbBC8XGwQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3974026%2Forg%2F40b23b0aed0d79bebe03bf70b60f064c.jpg%2FVePIf3_WO3lw0pbUlC-v-WFeMZYCC3TcLxcbBC8XGwQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d0b2c2cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63f7ef702f145279f2e1987f03c807c7f152d9e1","tid":1869441,"uid":36383,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"訓示: 下次記得要捐 Csi"},{"pid":"5ed2a5028d43ade66e3941309b334bad98b71e9d","tid":1869441,"uid":127177,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"點解要訓示，支援武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何錯之有"},{"pid":"eb9183f86ee852726c049d034ffc2382f29a4b0c","tid":1869441,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ff74ca038f4ece87a01a085c248be373918f1e3","tid":1869441,"uid":201141,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"用警察名義<br />\n與警隊無關<br />\n紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65915efd0c4550e3e30efc837f3d652af53e01b","tid":1869441,"uid":223233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"俾啲藍絲睇下<br />\n<br />\n撐警又點？人地奶中國，都唔捐俾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76717a9f59ce05d943402a2f85bcb6816ab3bbbe","tid":1869441,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"我愛國無罪!!!<br />\n起立! 敬禮!哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7ed0d90426864214992334c2e8218ef478cd36","tid":1869441,"uid":6058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"公職人員行為失當罪<br />\n仲有貪污"},{"pid":"f0a50c361e2f6bbed9df75c5e15c4bae38597483","tid":1869441,"uid":258258,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"警員立場不代表警局立埸<br />\n警局立場不代表警務處立場<br />\n警務處立場不代表鄧火丙立場<br />\n鄧火丙立場不代表警員立場<br />\n警員行為言論不代表警員立場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於兜到"},{"pid":"14d27354723d86cc73e1846ab99803ad5797d5bf","tid":1869441,"uid":268121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc938e5c5e6c35b09a0cce485a808b600cf9272e","tid":1869441,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"開佢箱一定斷正"},{"pid":"80c8d993a41e3fbf0453aa5c217f0ac45295caa8","tid":1869441,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"親身上去啦 <br />\n冇d誠意"},{"pid":"61827c9130241340b530d0c4503ee70ae6d27440","tid":1869441,"uid":238415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"警察名義 = 個人身份<br />\n仲有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879f812339f946f0c13a3f1e25dbf4caa9189c3e","tid":1869441,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，涉事報稱「海港sir」人士，相信為現任沙田警區助理指揮官陳凱港。根據陳凱港過去接受內地傳媒的訪問，職級為警司的陳凱港微博網名為「@海港SirHabaSir」，其微博「粉絲數」在去年底已達16萬，被形容香港警察中的「網紅」。<br />\n<br />\n陳凱港昨日在其個人facebook專頁中承認事件，指「因為私自購買了韓國製造KF94口罩捐贈武漢及香港醫院，為同僚帶來麻煩及損害組織聲譽。本人將停止所有社交媒體上發聲和發佈，並保持低調。」<br />\n<br />\n不少撐警人士在fb留言為陳凱港抱不平；亦有網民留言不點名指「光頭警長」咒罵醫護的言論，及俗稱「散仔會」的警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉，公開指責政務司司長的行為，均毫無紀律，質疑為何二人未被訓示。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署生產標示有CSi字樣的口罩，雖然只供政府內部使用，不過再有網民在facebook群組報稱，有家人以每包100元價錢買到一包有CSi字樣的口罩，並附上一包口罩的圖片，但未有披露交易日期、購買地點及賣家等資料，未能判斷真偽。<br />\n<br />\n而懲教署「更生先鋒計畫」facebook專頁，昨日亦貼出一批懲教人員協助生產口罩的圖片，網民隨即紛紛留言「2盒，thx」向懲教署求口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200208/7KCBAMERQXLUFYQHFWNLLLEGME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2WK386StODFvE1bexinUbEWDz4NQsUyR-3vwzv6NMtYB36imdoXPaOYYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2F7KCBAMERQXLUFYQHFWNLLLEGME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2WK386StODFvE1bexinUbEWDz4NQsUyR-3vwzv6NMtYB36imdoXPaOYYM&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=74b8940d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2F7KCBAMERQXLUFYQHFWNLLLEGME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2WK386StODFvE1bexinUbEWDz4NQsUyR-3vwzv6NMtYB36imdoXPaOYYM&h=14074243\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200208/7KCBAMERQXLUFYQHFWNLLLEGME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2WK386StODFvE1bexinUbEWDz4NQsUyR-3vwzv6NMtYB36imdoXPaOYYM</a>"},{"pid":"16f6ba9eaf05b5e43529b6e6763d61459d5cd3e0","tid":1869441,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61827c9130241340b530d0c4503ee70ae6d27440","tid":1869441,"uid":238415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"警察名義 = 個人身份<br />\n仲有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"著住狗衫訪問都可以話個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbf90bee8c9fb81b46e0bc9b8112ddc11b86b4e","tid":1869441,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"警員係警隊一份子，  團結精神去左邊？"},{"pid":"f8914295045a3f67168355d7687a84e63e433bb3","tid":1869441,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"認喇<br />\n不過係偷姐"},{"pid":"6040202bb30c4103251d49ac64817a153139684d","tid":1869441,"uid":175679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea558d67d24015221ee0eb0265c929d96f6732b2","tid":1869441,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"On9 都做到警司 十幾萬個月 <br />\n呢個政府究竟用咗幾多錢養垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}